<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV17">
<l>iruḷvirin tālaṉṉa mānīrt tiraikoṇṭu vāḻiyarō</l>
<l>viruḷpirin tālaṉpar tērvaḻi tūra laravaṇaimē</l>
<l>liruḷviri nīlak karunā yiṟucuṭar kālvatupō</l>
<l>liruḷviri cōtip perumā ṉuṟaiyu meṟikaṭalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With waves of water dark like darkness expanded, may you live,</l>
<l>when he separates in the dark, don’t fill up the tracks of [my] lover’s chariot,</l>
<l>dashing ocean, where the great lord of darkly expanding lustre stays,</l>
<l>like glow flowing from a blue-black sun expanding in the dark</l>
<l>						on the serpent bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
